duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide patient care and administer medications and treatments.
Maintain accurate patient records and monitor patient condition.
Assist in medical procedures and surgeries.
Educate patients and families about treatment plans and aftercare.
Collaborate with other healthcare professionals to ensure holistic patient care.

education_certification.credential: Associate Degree in Nursing. Advanced Cardiac Life Support (ACLS) and Basic Cardiac Life Support (BCLS) certifications
